name: Battle Axe, 80cm
description: The Battle Axe in foam and latex is a weapon for LARP or Cosplay event. 85cm long with a large, bearded blade, it has reach and power.

name: Wood Axe, 85cm
description: The Wood Axe in Foam and Latex is a weapon for LARP and Cosplay. Inspired by the lumberjack's tool, it has a great reach and swing that will confound and kill your enemies.

name: Orc Larp Axe, 90cm
description: The Orc Axe in latex and foam is a great choice for LARP and Cosplay. A sturdy weapon with a broad ax blade, it will add some grit to any orc or barbarian character.

name: Orc Big Axe, 150cm
description: The Orc Big Axe is a two handed weapon for LARP and Cosplay. Its wide, savage blade will intimidate your enemies. Designed for Barbarians and Orcs.

name: Dark Elf War Axe, 90cm
description: The drow war axe is a foam and latex weapon for LARP and cosplay. A 80cm long ax forged in the under dark by the sickest dark elven smiths, it will give a malevolent edge to your character.

name: Dark Elf Larp Axe, 65cm
description: The Dark Elf Axe is a foam %26 latex weapon for your drow character in a LARP or Cosplay event. Compact, fast yet deadly, this ax will help you carry a slaughter!

name: War Scythe, 60cm
description: The War Scythe is a Foam and Latex axe for LARP and Cosplay. It's a hand sickle, 60cm long, perfect for monk or peasant characters.

name: Dane Axe, 150cm
description: The Dane Axe is a Foam %26 Latex weapon for LARP %26 cosplay. A viking two-handed weapon with incredible reach, speed and violence, it will inspire terror in your victims.

name: Viking Axe, 55cm
description: The Viking Axe in Foam and Latex is a weapon for LARP and Cosplay. This Norsemen's axe will perform greatly in a shield wall, with its bearded blade and light weight.

name: Cleaver Axe, 70cm
description: The Cleaver axe is a fantasy foam %26 latex weapon for LARP and Cosplay. Its jagged looks, good reach and speed makes it a perfect boarding axe for pirates and swashbucklers.

name: Hand Axe, 55cm
description: The Hand Axe in Foam and Latex is a perfect side weapon for your LARP %26 Cosplay character. An affordable %26 dependable choice for an adventurer who need a second weapon.

name: Executioner Axe, 85cm
description: The executioner axe in Foam and Latex is a great weapon for LARP and Cosplay. Its chiseled blade and twisted steel shaft will help you kill with style.

name: Double Headed Battle Axe, 85cm
description: The Double Headed axe in foam and latex is a great weapon for LARP and Cosplay. This Barbarian axe exudes power and savagery.

name: Single Bladed Axe, 105cm
description: This huge single bladed axe is a menacing threat on any battlefield. Hand painted to perfection this latex war axe shows signs of battle so do not expect perfection. This 2 handed ax can only be wielded by the mightiest of larp warriors.
